    java.io.Serializable
    public class User
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    In the User model class you can 1. get user name and user albums 2. Add/Remove albums 3. Add photos to album 4. Retrieve album index number and album name 5. Checks if album name already exists
